settings.description: Larry got a new airship and also he added a bonus room too, your mission is to defeat Larry. Now do it or everybody in toad town will cry.
Mario found a fort, and finds out that bowser is inside, will he defeat bowser and escape alive? Or will he fail and lose a life?
Pulley Platforms react to the Mario Bros.'s weight. Always keep an eye on both platforms at the same time and make sure you have the room you need to jump!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!
